<div class="container">
	<div class="row">

		<div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
			<h1 class="text-center">Explore</h1>
				<div class="questions">
					<div class="q1">
						<h3>Imagine that you have achieved your goal and are that successful version of yourself now. What can you see, hear and feel? â€“ really associate yourself.</h3>

						<p>Describe, in as much detail as possible what you are seeing.</p>
						
						<%= form_for @assessment do |f| %>
							<% if @assessment.errors.any? %>
								<div class="notice">
								<p>There was a problem:</p>
								<% @assessment.errors.full_messages.each do |msg| %>
									<li><%= msg %></li>
								<% end %>
							<% end %>	

							<p class="form-group">
								<%= f.text_area :q1, size: "20x7", placeholder: "Where are you? What are you doing? Who is around you? Etc.", required: true, class: "form-control" %>
							</p>

					</div><!--/q1 -->					

					<h3>Now visualize the steps you took to get there, including the point where you are now, making that initial decision.</h3> 

					<p>Write down the steps you took</p>

					<p class="form-group">
						<%= f.text_area :q2, size: "20x7", required: true, class: "form-control" %>
					</p>					

					  <div class="form-group text-right">
					    <%= f.submit "Save", class: "btn btn-success btn-lg" %>
					  </div>
					<% end %>
				</div><!-- /questions -->
			</div><!-- /col-sm-6 -->
		</div><!-- /col-sm-8 -->	

	</div><!-- /row -->	
	<%= link_to "Back", user_path(current_user) %>		
</div><!-- /container -->